name: The Pyramids
description:
The scan of the ancient pyramids, which are located deep underground at a depth of around 15,000 kilometres, was obtained using ETH/TEZ technology; no one knows who built the pyramids and how they were built.

I only managed to take 25 scans, so they are yours. The pyramids were later destroyed beneath the earth's crust.
